<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. nicobarica" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" rank="species" species="nicobarica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">H. nicobarica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Annandale, 1909, 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. gigas" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" rank="species" species="gigas">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">H. gigas</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Annandale, 1905 and 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. cygnus" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" rank="species" species="cygnus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">H. cygnus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Pilsbry, 1907 could be invalid species and future revision may synonymize some or all of them. 
<bibRefCitation author="Zullo, VA" journalOrPublisher="Pacific Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" pagination="355 - 72" refId="B80" refString="Zullo, VA, Newman, WA, 1964. Thoracic Cirripedia from a SE Pacific Guyot. Pacific Science 18: 355 - 72" title="Thoracic Cirripedia from a SE Pacific Guyot." volume="18" year="1964">Zullo and Newman (1964)</bibRefCitation>
